behavior clean_vegetable(vegetable:item, sink:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inside(vegetable, sink)
        # Ensure the vegetable is placed inside the sink

        if exists faucet:item: is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            # Turn on the faucet if it is next to the sink

        wash(vegetable) # Wash the vegetable

        if exists faucet:item: is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)
            # Turn off the faucet after cleaning

def is_pot_near_stove(pot:item):
    # Determine whether the pot is near the stove
    symbol is_pot_near_stove = exists stove:item: is_stove(stove) and close(pot, stove)
    return is_pot_near_stove

behavior transfer_vegetables(pot:item, vegetables:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(vegetables, pot) # Transfer vegetables into the pot

behavior boil_on_stove(pot:item, stove:item, vegetables:item):
    body:
        assert is_pot_near_stove(pot)
        # Ensure pot is near the stove
        achieve_once is_on(stove) # Turn on the stove
        achieve has_water(pot) # Ensure pot has water
        # Assume the pot reaches boiling temperature by achieving is_on condition
        achieve has_water(vegetables) # Ensure vegetables absorb water while boiling

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove)
        # Select a stove
        
        bind pot: item where:
            is_pot(pot)
        # Select a pot

        bind food_vegetable: item where:
            is_food_vegetable(food_vegetable) and clean(food_vegetable)
        # Select clean vegetables

        transfer_vegetables(pot, food_vegetable) 
        
        if not is_pot_near_stove(pot):
            move(pot) # Move pot close to the stove if not already near
        
        boil_on_stove(pot, stove, food_vegetable)

behavior put_vegetables_in_pot(vegetables:item, pot:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(vegetables, pot)

behavior boil_vegetables(pot:item, stove:item):
    body:
        achieve on(pot, stove)
        achieve plugged(stove)
        achieve is_on(stove)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind vegetables: item where:
            is_food_vegetable(vegetables) and clean(vegetables)
        # Select the washed vegetables
        
        bind pot: item where:
            is_pot(pot)
        # Select a pot

        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove)
        # Select a stove

        put_vegetables_in_pot(vegetables, pot)
        boil_vegetables(pot, stove)
